ETHICAL USE GUIDELINES

While not legally binding, users are encouraged to:

1. Respect Content Creators
   - Support creators through official channels when possible
   - Don't redistribute downloaded content without permission
   - Consider the impact on content creators' livelihoods

2. Personal Use Only
   - Use downloads for personal enjoyment and backup
   - Don't use for commercial purposes without proper licensing
   - Don't circumvent paywalls or premium content restrictions

3. Fair Use Consideration
   - Understand fair use principles in your jurisdiction
   - Use content in transformative ways when appropriate
   - Give credit to original creators

4. Platform Respect
   - Don't abuse or overload platform servers
   - Respect rate limits and access restrictions
   - Don't use for automated mass downloading

5. Privacy
   - Don't download private or restricted content
   - Respect privacy settings and access controls
   - Don't share personal information obtained through downloads

